VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT HiveAesCipher\s*\(|Hive\.generateSecureKey\s*\(\s*\)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:flutter_secure_storage|FlutterSecureStorage|SecureStoragePlugin
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Hive AES cipher key usage without secure storage for the key material.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Hive Encryption Key Stored Insecurely.
